WEBVTT

00:04.588 --> 00:05.881
<i>Previously on</i> The Affair...

00:05.964 --> 00:07.299
I don't want to have to pay
the rent by myself every month.

00:07.382 --> 00:10.135
Let's just go get married
at city hall tonight.

00:10.219 --> 00:11.970
I want a wedding,
at my grandparents' house.

00:12.054 --> 00:13.931
Whitney, this marriage thing,

00:14.014 --> 00:15.307
you don't have to do it,
you know.

00:15.390 --> 00:16.225
But, actually, Dad, I do,
because if I don't,

00:16.308 --> 00:18.560
then Colin has to leave
the country.

00:18.644 --> 00:22.397
I'm desperate for a date
to my opening tomorrow.

00:22.481 --> 00:24.733
- Dashiell Boucicault.
‐ Hi.

00:24.816 --> 00:26.818
<i>He likes to watch.</i>

00:26.902 --> 00:29.738
<i>He could give you a gallery.</i>

00:29.821 --> 00:30.864
‐ I'm married.
‐Thank you

00:30.948 --> 00:32.406
for finally telling me.

00:32.491 --> 00:34.535
‐That's it?
‐What do you want me to say?

00:34.618 --> 00:35.494
Doesn't matter.
You love me, too.

00:35.577 --> 00:39.081
Oh, it does matter.
And I don't forgive you.

00:39.164 --> 00:41.583
And how can I tell you I love
you? I don't even know you.

